org.mini2Dx.core.collision

Class CollisionBox

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mini2Dx.core.geom.Shape
      • org.mini2Dx.core.geom.Rectangle
        • org.mini2Dx.core.collision.CollisionBox
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CollisionArea, CollisionObject, Positionable, PositionChangeListener<CollisionBox>, Sizeable, SizeChangeListener<CollisionBox>, Interpolatable, org.mini2Dx.gdx.utils.Disposable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    QuadTreeAwareCollisionBox

    public class CollisionBox
extends Rectangle
implements CollisionArea, PositionChangeListener<CollisionBox>, SizeChangeListener<CollisionBox>
    An implementation of Rectangle that allows for interpolation. Game objects can use this class to move around the game world and retrieve the appropriate rendering coordinates during the render phase.
